                "data": {
                  "inline": [
                    {
                      "type": "Words",
                      "data": {
                        "value": "If a float, this defines the aspect ratio (i.e. the ratio height / width). In case of an array the aspect ratio is number of rows / number of columns, so that the array could be fitted in the figure undistorted."
